Interface DomWrapper

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Attribute, CData, Comment, Content, DocType, Document, DocumentFragment, Element, Namespace, ProcessingInstruction, Text

    public interface DomWrapper
    Interface to provide access to a wrapped dom4j Node.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      DomWrapper detach()
      Detach the underlying dom4j Node.
      org.dom4j.Node getNodeObject()
      Returns the Node that the implementing class is wrapping.
      Element getParentElement()
      Returns the parent Element or null if it is the root element or does not support the parent relationship.
